params.text: DOOMU FOOWÉKAAY BU RÉER
Ki moy Abi ak doomu foowékaayam.
Abi dafa bëgg doomam.
Abi dafa bëgg foo ak doomam.
Doomu Abi bi dafa réer.
Abi dafay set doomam.
Xol na ci suufu tabaal bi.
Xol na ci suufu sees bi.
Xol na ci suufu ci négg bi.
Xol na ci suufu ci sardéŋ.
Abi lacc na muus bi “ Ana sama doom bi? ”
Muus bi wax “ Meew ”
Abi lacc na ginaar gu jiggéen gi “ Ana sama doom bi? ”
Ganaar gu jiggéen gi wax na Abi “ Ku – ku – ku ” .
Abi lacc na xaj bi “ Ana sama doom bi? ”
Xaj bi wax “ Bow wow ” . Xaj bi gisoon na doom bi.

"DOOMU FOOWÉKAAY BU RÉER" credits

This work, "DOOMU FOOWÉKAAY BU RÉER", is a derivative of "The Lost Doll" as translated by Alisha Berger and used under CC BY. The © for this translation lies with Room to Read, 2015. "DOOMU FOOWÉKAAY BU RÉER" is based on the original story: 'Umdoli Lolahlekile', by Moleboge Shibboleth Poho. © Room to Read, 2015.
